Class SeriesViewFunction<I,O>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataListener, DataSeries<O>, DataSet, SeriesView<O>, View, Iterable<O>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CalcSeries

    public abstract class SeriesViewFunction<I,O>
extends AbstractSeriesView<I,O>
    Base class for creating DataSeries that are calculated from zero, one or more other DataSeries. If input series are provided then change events on those series are forwarded to this series.
    Author:
    O. J. Coleman
